beer.beer_description:
We've taken the bright malt sweetness of a Helles Lager and combined it with the subtle bitterness of a Pilsner and made a super refreshing, beautifully balanced lager. A Dortmund Export, for sunny summer days in Oz. Our Export showcases a golden hue that captivates the senses.

The original blue collar knock off beer, full flavour with smooth refreshing drinkability. Designed to reach parts that others can't get to.
